- All tests pass with `pnpm vitest run apps/client/src/layers/features/status/__tests__/PermissionModeItem.test.tsx`
- Tests cover: all 6 modes rendering, capability filtering, current mode display, mode selection callback, disabled state, dontAsk display, auto display
- No test uses arbitrary timeouts or empty waitFor callbacks
- `pnpm typecheck` passes

